DataSet.Name: BFT
DataSet.Description: BFT DataSet that contains the definitions of the raw dimensions and measures from various sources.

DataTable.Name: SMLCidAndUserSeg
DataTable.Description: BFT data source view definition of the CID + UserSeg + QuerySeg join

DataTable.Name: SMLSLAPI
DataTable.Description: SLAPI definition of SML dimensions and measures used by BFT

Property.Name: ScopeView
Property.Value: VIEW "/shares/searchDM/distrib/released/BFT/BFTSearchView/BFTSearchView.view" PARAMS ( StartDate = @@StartDate@@, EndDate = @@EndDate@@,Columns = "@@Columns@@", AggMode = @@AggMode@@, FailoverTo="CacheOrView", SamplePercent=-1)

DataColumn.Name: UnifiedOSName
DataColumn.Definition: IF(Metrics_OSProductName.ToLower() == "windows phone", DataMining.ScopeUtilities.LookupHelper.TableLookupIgnoreCase("SearchAdCenterUnifiedOSConsolidationList.tsv", 0, true, Metrics_OSProductName + " " + Metrics_OSMajorVersion + "." + Metrics_OSMinorVersion, 1, "other"), DataMining.ScopeUtilities.LookupHelper.TableLookupIgnoreCase("SearchAdCenterUnifiedOSConsolidationList.tsv", 0, true, Metrics_OSProductName, 1, "other"))

DataColumn.Name: UnifiedOSVersion
DataColumn.Definition: IF(Metrics_OSProductName.ToLower() == "windows phone", DataMining.ScopeUtilities.LookupHelper.TableLookupIgnoreCase("SearchAdCenterUnifiedOSConsolidationList.tsv", 0, true, Metrics_OSProductName + " " + Metrics_OSMajorVersion + "." + Metrics_OSMinorVersion, 2, "other"), DataMining.ScopeUtilities.LookupHelper.TableLookupIgnoreCase("SearchAdCenterUnifiedOSConsolidationList.tsv", 0, true, Metrics_OSProductName, 2, "other"))

DataColumn.Name: QueryMinute
DataColumn.Definition: new DateTime(Request_RequestTime.Year, Request_RequestTime.Month, Request_RequestTime.Day, Request_RequestTime.Hour, Request_RequestTime.Minute, 0, Request_RequestTime.Kind)

DataColumn.Name: QueryHour
DataColumn.Definition: new DateTime(Request_RequestTime.Year, Request_RequestTime.Month, Request_RequestTime.Day, Request_RequestTime.Hour, 0, 0, Request_RequestTime.Kind)

DataColumn.Name: UserIsNewDaily
DataColumn.Definition: IF(User_IsNew AND (NOT usLast35DaysVisitedDayCount.HasValue OR usLast35DaysVisitedDayCount.Value == 1), true, false)

DataColumn.Name: UserSearchIntensity
DataColumn.Definition: IF(string.Equals(usSearchIntensity, "high", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase) OR string.Equals(usSearchIntensity, "medium", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase) OR string.Equals(usSearchIntensity, "low", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase), usSearchIntensity, "NotApplicable")

DataTable.Name: SMLUnifiedInternal
DataTable.Description: BFT data source view for the SML-ACML Unified internal data stream
